==English==
=== Etymology ===
Probably patterned after [[octogenarian]]; With the Latin ''[[quattor]]'' "four" in it's prefix form ''[[quadra-]]''

=== Adjective ===
'''quadragenarian'''
# between the [[age]]s of 40 and 49; in one's [[fifth]] [[decade]]

=== Noun ===
'''quadragenarian'''
# one who is quadragenarian

